reviews.text: We caught a train back from London yesterday but there had been a few power outages at stations along the way due to flooding. We’re not familiar with the area but the young man working at the station helped us to figure out the best route back and what trains were still running. He even talked the the conductor on the train we were getting on to make sure that we got off at the right stations- such above and beyond service!
Been going here for years, great station.

reviews.text: Haslemere is located in the town with the same name and is served by Southwest Trains, Haslemere is a great station, staff are helpful and trains are on team, there is a car parts store nearby and I like the station building, the station is pretty cool and among one of my favourites.
